## Requirements

+ Python >= 3.6
+ numpy >= 1.12.1
+ seaborn >= 0.9
+ matplotlib >= 2.2.2
+ pandas >= 0.23.0
+ scipy >= 1.1.0
+ statsmodels (optional, for multiple testing corrections)


